According to Sembcorp Silulumanzi they have oficially ran dry at Waterkloof reservoir. This is due to several incidents of load shedding and prolonged unplanned outages on March 18, coupled with transformer failures on March 19. • The Rest Eco Estates, Batheleur, The Edge and areas of Uitsig Landgoed • Several other reservoirs incl Steiltes, Sonheuwel, Stonehenge and West Acres are critically low. Sembcorp Silulumanzi also expressed that the public must use water sparingly during this time.